<D>__{only because i got pulled out early.}
<C>__{deane}
<D>__{nobody else ever got anywhere near him. nobody else... understands him like you do.}
<A>__{parker, looking at her incredulously, moves his index finger circularly, as in get on with it, already. cox opens a folder and shows parker several photographs of reilly, or what was left of him.}
<C>__{cox}
<D>__{these were taken inside letac an hour ago. pretty pictures, aren't they?}
